casebody.data:
Banta, Appellant, v. Hoggitiris, Bespondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 4, 1892.) Appeal from special term. Action by Nancy E. Banta against P. Hoggitiris.

Argued before Bookstaver, Bischoff, and Pryor, JJ.

R. T. B. Easton, for appellant. A. C. Eransioli, for respondent.

No opinion. Order reversed, with costs.
